{"content": "I'll solve this step-by-step using the conversion method.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 678\u2089 to base 10**\n678\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070\n= 6\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 8\u00d71\n= 486 + 63 + 8\n= 557\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 286\u2089 to base 10**\n286\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 8\u00d79\u00b9 + 6\u00d79\u2070\n= 2\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 6\u00d71\n= 162 + 72 + 6\n= 240\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n557\u2081\u2080 \u00d7 240\u2081\u2080 = 133,680\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 133,680\u2081\u2080 to base 9**\n133,680 \u00f7 9 = 14,853 R 3\n14,853 \u00f7 9 = 1,650 R 3\n1,650 \u00f7 9 = 183 R 3\n183 \u00f7 9 = 20 R 3\n20 \u00f7 9 = 2 R 2\n2 \u00f7 9 = 0 R 2\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 223333\u2089\n\n**Step 5: Verify**\n223333\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u2075 + 2\u00d79\u2074 + 3\u00d79\u00b3 + 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 3\u00d79\u00b9 + 3\u00d79\u2070\n= 2\u00d759049 + 2\u00d76561 + 3\u00d7729 + 3\u00d781 + 3\u00d79 + 3\n= 118098 + 13122 + 2187 + 243 + 27 + 3\n= 133,680\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n223333", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 889, "completion_tokens": 507}